额、违法所得金额认定有误,量罚不当。综上,当事人请求不予行政处罚。\n经复核,我会认为:一是综合内幕信息形成公开过程、联络接触时点、买入与卖出时点、交易量、交', 'siteName': '中国证券监督管理委员会官网', 'siteIcon': 'https://th.bochaai.com/favicon?domain_url=http://www.csrc.gov.cn/csrc/c101928/c7621301/content.shtml', 'datePublished': '2026-03-20T18:30:40+08:00', 'dateLastCrawled': '2026-03-20T18:30:40Z', 'cachedPageUrl': None, 'language': None, 'isFamilyFriendly': None, 'isNavigational': None}], 'someResultsRemoved': True}, 'images': {'id': None, 'readLink': None, 'webSearchUrl': None, 'value': [{'webSearchUrl': None, 'name': None, 'thumbnailUrl': 'https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/QfQGvlbtugBeDgs.jpg', 'datePublished': None, 'contentUrl': 'https://i.17173cdn.com/2fhnvk/YWxqaGBf/cms3/QfQGvlbtugBeDgs.jpg', 'hostPageUrl': 'https://news.17173.com/content/03212026/080133244.shtml', 'contentSize': None, 'encodingFormat': None, 'hostPageDisplayUrl': 'https://news.17173.com/content/03212026/080133244.shtml', 'width': 0, 'height': 0, 'thumbnail': None}, {'webSearchUrl': None, 'name': None, 'thumbnailUrl': 'https://img.ithome.com/images/v2/t.png', 'datePublished': None, 'contentUrl': 'https://img.ithome.com/images/v2/t.png', 'hostPageUrl': 'https://www.ithome.com/0/931/199.htm', 'contentSize': None, 'encodingFormat': None, 'hostPageDisplayUrl': 'https://www.ithome.com/0/931/199.htm', 'width': 0, 'height': 0, 'thumbnail': None}], 'isFamilyFriendly': None}, 'videos': None}}
